The Telegraph - Calcutta : Opinion
		 Monday, May 26, 2003 				 Traffic-light repair sponsors rejected
		 SNARL TIME: Traffic jams are a regular  feature on BT Road. Pictures by Kishor Roy ChowdhurySoma Chowdhury: The traffic lights at Kamarhati, Panihati and Dunlop are defunct. Often, traffic police are missing. Jams and related problems are regular affairs in the area. Is there no way out of this mess?																																																													We are short-staffed with traffic constables. However, that will be rectified. About the traffic signals, we need funds and for that, we had selected some sponsors, but the PWD has objected to it.
